    "## 3. Reinforcement Learning\n",
    "\n",
    "- Learning what to do and how to map **situations** to **actions**. \n",
    "- The **agent** is not told which action to take, but instead must discover which action will yield the maximum **reward (goal)**.Â The end result is to maximize the numerical reward signal. \n",
    "- Algorithm learns to react to an **environment**.\n",
    "- For instance: a toddler learning to walk, self driving cars,..\n",
    "\n",
    "\n"
   ]
